Package de.tudresden.inf.rn.mobilis.sea.jingle.connection.manager.observer

An auxiliary package defining classes to synchronize the asynchronous SmackX session establishment

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ReceptionListener
    A ReceptionListener may be created to handle Raw items (the item has to be cast to the corresponding type by yourself)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SessionObserver
    This auxiliary SessionObserver is used to lazy add ReceptionListeners and Raw media types when a JingleSession has been created (so you may add the prototypes and listeners at any time)
